<section class="about-contact">
  <div class="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <img src="/images/BowtieCharlie.jpg" alt="Popcorn Charlie" width="400" />

    <div>
      <h4>Personalized Service:</h4>
      <p>
        We also take special requests. If you want a flavor that is out of season or only available
        upon request, we will make it for you! The only catch is: you have to meet a minimum purchase
        amount:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>$20 for Savory Flavors</li>
        <li>$30 for Candied Flavors</li>
        <li>$35 for Candied+ Flavors</li>
        <li>$40 for Premium Candied Flavors</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4>Committed to Quality</h4>
      <p><!-- content to be filled in --></p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4>100% Satisfaction Guaranteed</h4>
      <p>
        Our popcorn is guaranteed fresh for one month after the packaged date. We want you to be
        completely satisfied, so if you experience any issues with the product, please contact us
        right away so we can address the problem.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="contact">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>

    <div>
      <h4>"Popcorn Charlie" and Company</h4>
      <p>3601 North Division Street, Davenport, Iowa 52806, United States</p>
      <a href="tel:5633889555">563-388-9555</a>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4>Hours</h4>
      <p>Open today: 10:00 am – 06:00 pm</p>
      <!-- TODO: full weekly hours -->
    </div>

    <form>
